*To make a popup*

Open Script editor
Type "display dialog "Enter your text here...""
Run the script.
If typed right you should see similar results to example 1 (Find it in the examples folder)

*To add different options to your popup*

Type "display dialog "Enter your text here..." buttons {"Choice 1", "Choice 2"}"
Run the script.
If typed right you should see similar results to example 2 (Find it in the examples folder)

*To add actions to your buttons*

type "if the button returned of the result is "Choice 1" then (put your action here)"
then type "else" and then the action for the second button.
